    "title": "Sehirou.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Sehirou has a skeletal white body with sparrow-like wings and a brain for a head. It dribbles constantly.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 144     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++       </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++++ +    </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: ++.     </lightgrey><darkgrey>   rC: ...      </darkgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: High    </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 140% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 63% to hit with your +9 bardiche of entangling.\nIt has about 9% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage  \nHit     46          \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to steam and miasma.\nIt is vulnerable to silver and hated by Zin.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.",
